                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">So what about the other trials? One day while Execution was full, we decided to try one of the other trials, in this case Lashing. I have yet to do this successfully and would love to know some good strategies on it and any other trial for that matter. 
<br />

<br />
We tried to use the same strategy that we used for execution on Lashing, but the untargetable guy is also unstunnable. After a short time either the cleric or I would have enough agro that one of us would get killed before the 3 spirits could be finished.
<br />

<br />
We did learn to keep the healer, the chanter, and the main assist to stay with the main assault, and assign everyone else a spirit to kill as soon as the lasher spawned, so tehy would stop what they were doing and kill it, then come back to get rid of the lasher quickly. Any other tips for this or any other trial?</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
